OL,3,CParliament restoration plans revealed
OL,4,Cwith costs of up to #40 billion
OL,6,FMajor restoration plans for the Palace
OL,7,Fof Westminster have been presented to
OL,8,FMPs and peers, with one option
OL,9,Fexpected to rack up a bill of nearly
OL,10,F#40 billion.
OL,12,FTwo options have been put forward: one
OL,13,Ffor a "full decant", which would see
OL,14,Fboth houses of parliament move out of
OL,15,Fthe Palace of Westminster while works
OL,16,Ftake place; and another where the
OL,17,Fpalace would be worked on in stages.
