OL,3,CParliament restoration plans revealed
OL,4,Cwith costs of up to #40 billion
OL,6,FThe first would last 19 to 24 years
OL,7,Fand could cost up to #15.6 billion,
OL,8,Fwhile the other option would take 38
OL,9,Fto 61 years and cost up to #39.2
OL,10,Fbillion.
OL,12,FThose figures include inflation.
OL,14,FIn a report released on Thursday, the
OL,15,FRestoration and Renewal (R&R) Client
OL,16,FBoard argued that previous decisions
OL,17,Fto delay work "to avoid significant
OL,18,Fdisruption" has resulted in underlying
OL,19,Fissues "not being fully addressed".
