OL,3,CParliament restoration plans revealed
OL,4,Cwith costs of up to #40 billion
OL,6,FThe report states: "Continuing in the
OL,7,Fsame way is unsustainable, will lead
OL,8,Fto an expensive managed decline of the
OL,9,FPalace of Westminster and will mean
OL,10,Fincreasing safety and operational
OL,11,Frisks."
OL,13,FAt present, #1.5 million is spent per
OL,14,Fweek maintaining and repairing the
OL,15,FPalace of Westminster.
OL,17,FProblems in the last month alone
OL,18,Fincluded a heating failure in a key
OL,19,Fpart of the House of Lords, issues
OL,20,Fwith the sewage system, and numerous
OL,21,Ftoilets being out of action.
