OL,3,CParliament restoration plans revealed
OL,4,Cwith costs of up to #40 billion
OL,6,FThat work could start in 2026 if
OL,7,Fapproved.
OL,9,FThe board will then ask them to choose
OL,10,Fbetween the final two options by mid-
OL,11,F2030.
OL,13,FPhase one works include refurbishing
OL,14,Fthe inside of the Victoria Tower,
OL,15,Fbuilding a jetty on the Thames for
OL,16,Fdeliveries by river and starting
OL,17,Funderground construction on tunnel
OL,18,Fshafts.
